Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.40,0:00:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停止倒退
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.93,0:00:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.90,0:00:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前为止 没什么危险的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.38,0:00:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 真的没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.85,0:00:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 破废铁会将鲸乌贼全部消灭的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.96,0:00:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.77,0:00:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破废铁 雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.66,0:00:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.10,0:00:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认栖息于该海域的希迪亚斯已全部歼灭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.57,0:00:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 干得好！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.08,0:00:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 把人形机器人全部开出来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.69,0:00:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传说中的宝物是我们的了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.17,0:00:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢！
